" /><br />\n畫得比較差<br />\n樓主意思應該係咁<br />\n前面條友過完第一個燈唔行前少少頂住後面啲人"},{"pid":"0152fd6f2e5799eda1c80a74fef6a6e1340e9cb2","tid":341761,"uid":754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"成日都有啲咁嘅廢老廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一踩上行人路就剎掣 完全冇理過後面啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abb36b6ed599482041505a9146b1e53db6c4482","tid":341761,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/145439_d1cb1c204047124c913a1c2deba5e611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F145439_d1cb1c204047124c913a1c2deba5e611.jpg&h=5c56ce5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫得比較差<br />\n樓主意思應該係咁<br />\n前面條友過完第一個燈唔行前少少頂住後面啲人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明樓主講咩<br />\n<br />\n有兩條連續既馬路，通常第一條著綠燈，第二條都著紅燈。所以d人一過左第一條馬路就要企係到等<br />\n<br />\n企係到等冇問題，但問題係個安全島咁大，又唔撚行入d等，一定要企係個路口到等，於是阻住哂d人<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似上巴士d人唔行入d咁"},{"pid":"e26b736b24ddebd46e0af8798df027c431cc2c68","tid":341761,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"仲有上/落電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻撞鳩佢<br />\nBtw有埋圖仲唔明真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c02898c3ceb1f747d83e529b0349ddb9d39e7de","tid":341761,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有上/落電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻撞鳩佢<br />\nBtw有埋圖仲唔明真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一眼就明，因為我有遇過類似情況<br />\n<br />\n上面話唔明既，可能未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3506c5412f1a08f18972633b7ae97c5410276f","tid":341761,"uid":2896,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌唔怪得中文都有人可以拎U</blockquote><br />\n又唔怪得人，睇唔明果啲都係咁上下<br />\n五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3859a8ac8dd4f4586b0aae284f66ca3d3e320e0f","tid":341761,"uid":105410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"我住果頭班廢老都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢自己一到安全島就停<br />\n後面成班人半個身企左出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3d8e51a19240025eea55aba8289d842fdf5971","tid":341761,"uid":4934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"睇晒咁多個回覆先明樓主表達緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係咁？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/151911_964d4c517e4b46457402aa2a8a89ca8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F151911_964d4c517e4b46457402aa2a8a89ca8e.jpg&h=57d713e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}